1. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper focuses on the performance analysis of a drone cell in a communication network, which falls under the scope of networking and internet architecture. 
2. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper discusses the impact of interference on the uplink performance of a drone cell, which is related to information theory. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper analyzes the performance of a drone cell in a system that includes ground interferers, which falls under the scope of systems and control. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper discusses the transmission rate of the drone cell, which is related to multimedia applications. 
5. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper does not directly relate to cryptography and security, but it may indirectly impact the security of the communication network by analyzing the vulnerability of the drone cell to interference.
